# V3 User Guide

## Use Case
Java + React full stack merge conflicts.

## Prompt

Use Merge Conflict Agent V3.
Current branch: feature/customer-ui
Merged develop.
Balanced mode.
Enable Jira summary: No

## What Happens

1. Detect backend + frontend conflicts
2. Resolve Java / React / YAML / package conflicts
3. Run Maven/Gradle compile
4. Run npm build/tests
5. If failures occur:
   - Diagnose
   - Patch
   - Retry automatically
6. Repeat until pass or max loops reached
7. Generate reports

